OL,3,CGuernsey Finance open investigation
OL,4,Cafter alleged inappropriate behaviour
OL,6,FGuernsey Finance say the alleged
OL,7,Fbehaviour of two individuals involved
OL,8,Fin an incident widely shared on social
OL,9,Fmedia "falls significantly short" of
OL,10,Fthe standards they expect from
OL,11,Femployees.
OL,13,FIt comes after the organisation's CEO,
OL,14,FRupert Pleasant, resigned earlier this
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,FITV News understands the incident
OL,18,Fcentres around alleged inappropriate
OL,19,Fbehaviour captured in a recording of a
OL,20,Frecent staff training meeting.
