OL,3,CGuernsey Finance open investigation
OL,4,Cafter alleged inappropriate behaviour
OL,6,FThe recording purportedly captured a
OL,7,Fpersonal discussion and interaction
OL,8,Fbetween two people delivering the
OL,9,Ftraining after the session was over -
OL,10,Fone of whom was Mr Pleasant.
OL,12,FThe contents of this meeting were
OL,13,Fleaked and widely shared online.
OL,15,FGuernsey Finance markets the island's
OL,16,Ffinancial services industry.
OL,18,FIt is partially funded by the public,
OL,19,Fwith the States giving the agency more
OL,20,Fthan #1.5 million each year.
