OL,3,CGuernsey Finance open investigation
OL,4,Cafter alleged inappropriate behaviour
OL,6,FIn a statement issued this morning,
OL,7,Facting CEO Barnaby Molloy said an
OL,8,Findependent investigation into the
OL,9,Fincident is ongoing, adding:
OL,11,F"The alleged behaviour of the two
OL,12,Findividuals concerned falls
OL,13,Fsignificantly short of the standards
OL,14,Fwe expect.
OL,16,F"Any conversations and actions were
OL,17,Fclearly intended to be private; the
OL,18,Fbehaviour and opinions expressed do
OL,19,Fnot reflect those of our organisation.
