OL,3,CGuernsey Finance open investigation
OL,4,Cafter alleged inappropriate behaviour
OL,6,F"This matter is undoubtedly
OL,7,Fembarrassing for the individuals
OL,8,Finvolved, and we ask that their
OL,9,Fprivacy and that of their families be
OL,10,Frespected. We also want to acknowledge
OL,11,Four wider team and emphasise that this
OL,12,Fincident does not detract from the
OL,13,Fexcellent work done by our
OL,14,Forganisation every day."
OL,16,FThe statement further clarifies that
OL,17,Fthe individuals involved in the
OL,18,Fincident are no longer employed by
OL,19,FGuernsey Finance.
